data.description: PERRY HOMES NEW CONSTRUCTION READY FOR MOVE-IN! Two-story entry leads to open dining area, kitchen and family room. Wood look tile flooring throughout. Kitchen features corner walk-in pantry and generous island with built-in seating space. Family room with ceramic tile floor features wall of windows. Primary suite includes bedroom with 10-foot ceiling. Dual vanities, separate glass-enclosed shower and walk-in closet in primary bath. Two secondary bedrooms are downstairs. Upstairs features a game room and additional bedroom with full bathroom. Large windows add to this three-bedroom home. Covered backyard patio. Mud room off two-car garage.
